data.description: Fabulously upgraded, this amazing home is ready for its new owner! Boasting more than 3,600 square feet to hold even the largest family, you'll adore every inch of this property. With fruit trees out back, including peaches, pears and apples, with mature landscaping and an enormous backyard, you'll find peace and some self-sustainability, all in the heart of East Springfield! Kitchen plays host to granite countertops, over $5k worth of BRAND NEW black stainless appliances from Metro, that come with a transferrable warranty, as well as a portable island and breakfast nook. Formal dining boasts a built-in serviette, perfect for holiday get-togethers. Huge pantry off the kitchen! Large living area is light and bright, thanks to newer oversize windows and maintenance-free vinyl plank flooring. Focal point gas fireplace will keep you toasty all winter! Hall bath has been modernized, while keeping the aesthetic of the era intact. Master, with en suite bath, boasts a corner step-in shower, and the same fabulous granite countertops that flow throughout. Additional bedroom on the main level is ample-sized, with plenty of closet space. Downstairs, the walkout basement is a series of extra large spaces; another living area with its own fireplace and covered patio. This house is THE SPOT for entertaining! Additional living space, with access to the backyard, would be an awesome theater room, home gym, or gaming area, as it's currently being used. Bedroom, with its own full bath, is every teen's dream! Laundry and storage area in the basement is large enough for a workshop. If you want the utmost in SE Springfield living, look no further than this gem ... but see it soon, it won't last long!
